At Rainbow Learning Academy, we are based upon the principles of developmentally appropriate practice.
Our days are filled with enriching activities, exciting learning experiences, and wholesome meals and snacks.
Rainbow Learning Academy primary goal is to prepare your children for a life-long love of learning, and to instill self-confidence and self-esteem. Before you make your child care decision, please accept our invitation to visit in Bellevue.
http://rainbowlearningacademy.org/
